      • createVoiceChannel

        CompletableFuture<IGuildVoiceChannel> createVoiceChannel(String name,
                                                         int bitRate,
                                                         int userLimit,
                                                         IChannelCategory category,
                                                         IOverwrite... overwrites)
                                                  throws PermissionsException
        Creates a new VoiceChannel
        Parameters:
        name - The name of the channel
        bitRate - The channel's bitrate in kilobits per second (kbps). 1kb is equal to 1000bits (125Bytes). The bitrate is normalized to be within the range of 8 to 128kbps
        userLimit - The channel's userlimit with a maximum value of 99 users. A userLimit of 0 signifies no limit.
        category - The category to put the channel in
        overwrites - The channel's overwrites
        Returns:
        A future that completes with a new VoiceChannel Object if successful.
        Throws:
        PermissionsException
